data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS on the property and seller is requesting highest and best without escalation by 5pm February 7, 2024. Discover comfort and convenience at this Liberty Township 4-bed, 3-bath home on a wooded lot offering privacy and tranquility.  The heart of the home is a chef's kitchen, complete with modern appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the inviting living room, creating the perfect space for entertaining or enjoying quiet family moments. The master suite offers an ensuite retreat that you will find inviting. The backyard oasis features an in-ground swimming pool and hot tub with a large flat yard for outdoor activities. Schedule a tour to see the potential of this home!
